{"tid":512050,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知將來出路係點(2)","createTime":"2017-12-28T05:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T13:34:34.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0df9ab940b1ac53413fd2b892307a2e24352bbe","tid":512050,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T05:48:19.000Z","msg":"繼之前嘰post:<br />\n<br />\n呀媽唔想我一直留係屋企做低端人口，所以前日Boxing Day走左去約左個師奶朋友。之後大家一齊食飯，一路食一路係到問個朋友個仔做part time餐飲做成點，個仔話佢做野好忙，成日做野乜都要做斟茶遞水。問完之後呀媽一直「鼓勵」我去跟朋友去做，仲問佢地那邊仲請唔請人...不過自己一直好猶豫，始終自己只係個垃圾IT狗，除左間中幫呀媽洗碗外，連煮個飯都唔識，唔知自己有無能力做得到。不過如果我唔去做又搞到我好無用成個不孝子咁，而且呀爸話如果我咁介懷IT狗的話就直接話自己只係中六畢業，黑歷史左個學士學位去了...<br />\n<br />\nPS.都係一樣唔好叫我去見IT工，斟茶遞水係人，IT狗連曱甴都不如，老貓今日又話IT狗要洗成40萬進修啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634e8cd7e71fc78973c5ca001e0b1bb6fd888a3b","tid":512050,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88ecfce34d392ab36fc59cb288b2ad50064ad44","tid":512050,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc16d9b2a244841d913278acc2c381498026da2","tid":512050,"uid":164419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"